overviewContent: SEO practices have been applied to enhance search engine performance of web applications, with a focus on site speed, usability, and content structure. Meta tags were optimised and mobile responsiveness improved to achieve stronger visibility in Google search results. Structured data and advanced SEO techniques were implemented to boost indexing efficiency and user engagement. These measures contributed to higher organic traffic, improved rankings, and measurable business growth.
